            <trans-unit id="">
                <source>Help improve translate5: Allow screen recording in case of errors.<br /><br />For certain errors, the translate5 open-source development team can only reproduce and fix them if the user actions that led to the translate5 error are recorded as a video. Only what happens within translate5 will be recorded. The recording starts once a segment is opened for editing and stops as soon as the segment editing ends.<br /><br />The translate5 team would greatly appreciate it if you enable this feature – thank you in advance!<br /><br />Even when video recording is enabled, recordings will only be sent if you report an error that occurred.<br /><br />Videos associated with an error and sent to the server will be deleted as soon as they are no longer needed to fix the issue. The sole purpose of these videos is the development of translate5. The data will only be used for this purpose.<br /><br />For more information about video recording with theRootCause and data protection, please visit: https://confluence.translate5.net/x/EAArBw</source>
                <target>Help improve translate5: Allow screen recording in case of errors.<br /><br />For certain errors, the translate5 open-source development team can only reproduce and fix them if the user actions that led to the translate5 error are recorded as a video. Only what happens within translate5 will be recorded. The recording starts once a segment is opened for editing and stops as soon as the segment editing ends.<br /><br />The translate5 team would greatly appreciate it if you enable this feature – thank you in advance!<br /><br />Even when video recording is enabled, recordings will only be sent if you report an error that occurred.<br /><br />Videos associated with an error and sent to the server will be deleted as soon as they are no longer needed to fix the issue. The sole purpose of these videos is the development of translate5. The data will only be used for this purpose.<br /><br />For more information about video recording with theRootCause and data protection, please visit: https://confluence.translate5.net/x/EAArBw</target>
            </trans-unit>
